### **_Description_**

#### This app is for those who need to structure their weeks and workouts
#### User will be able to login with their Google account and once they have logged in it will prompted with "what their goals are"
#### App will be using this API: https://rapidapi.com/nabeeldev1340/api/workout-planner1/details

___
